  Introducción para el profesor                        
=================================================  -->
<introduction component="profesor">

  <!-- Estándares CCSS asociados -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="csss-leccion-titulo"/></title> 
    <p>K.CC.A.1, K.CC.B, K.CC.B.4, K.CC.B.5</p>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- índice de la lección (automático) -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="timeline-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <list-of elements="subsubsection reading-questions" scope="subsection"/>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Propósito de la lección -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="purpose-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>The purpose of this lesson is for students to count collections of objects. The focus is on students representing how they counted.</p>
  </paragraphs>

  <!-- Materiales requeridos -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="materials-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <p>Actividad de calentamiento</p>
        <xi:include href="./warm-preguntasNosotros-tableroAsistencia-mat.ptx"/>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Actividad 1</p>
        <xi:include href="./act-contemosColecciones-muestraCuantos-mat.ptx"/>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Actividad 2</p>
        <xi:include href="./act-preguntasTipoCuantos-mat.ptx"/>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Actividad 3</p>
        <xi:include href="./act-centros-escoger10-mat.ptx"/>
      </li>
    </ul> 
  </paragraphs>
  
  <!-- Introducción de la lección (narrative) -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="narrative-leccion-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>In the Questions About Us routine, students use 5-frames to determine how many students are at school today. Students then count objects in different collections in a way that makes sense to them and represent their collections. The second activity is an optional activity that provides support in keeping track of which objects have been counted.</p>
  </paragraphs>
  
  <!-- Preguntas de reflexión profesor -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="reflection-quest-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>As you finish up this unit, reflect on the norms and activities that have supported each student in learning math. List ways you have seen each student grow as a young mathematician throughout this work. List ways you have seen yourself grow as a teacher. What will you continue to do and what will you improve upon in Unit 2?</p>
  </paragraphs>
</introduction>


